        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Help for Moms and Babies Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows states to receive federal payment under Medicaid for outside services that are provided to pregnant and postpartum women who are substance use disorder patients at institutions for mental diseases.</p>]]></text>
